{"tid":129502,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"點解開始影相？","createTime":"2017-02-21T15:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T12:36:40.000Z","uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39b3ca63282fcd442b166484ee5e6ada5be53ed6","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:39:54.000Z","msg":"點解大家開始影相？影相又為乜野？你地影相既初心又係乜野？<br />\n<br />\n我就主要影人像，作品通常唔公開既，而且作品劣評如潮。<br />\n<br />\n點解開始影人，其實係之前幫朋友影過相，然後佢參加社運，然後要人幫手，所以我就開始影啦。我本身鐘意易Snap，但無可奈何我影人多啲人談論。<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔會當自己係攝影師，我係一個打雜。因為去到社運，資源缺乏，攝影往往同時係食焦，保護抗爭者，保護主角係首要過影相。而且，的確會影到五癆七傷，亦可能中椒中棍，肢體衝撞時有發生。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係之前既事，而家我就主要hea住影，因為真係唔知影相為乜咁。"},{"pid":"e7b2c42f350b23ee1cb569417bcfd71d2678c2b4","tid":129502,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"唔公開咁影黎做乜？"},{"pid":"ebf768636684b55b6628914afc71a02338bc068a","tid":129502,"uid":77747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔公開咁影黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n影黎自己J"},{"pid":"16fa224bab5a91683c924c2870cd69471bcbddcb","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔公開咁影黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n諗法唔同啦，又唔係要呃like<br />\n<br />\n如果影低左社運抗爭者既相又周圍貼<br />\n傳聞係會有blacklist既<br />\n<br />\n而且我見太多龍友當社運係影女活動<br />\n前面開晒旗<br />\n佢地可以慢慢討論枝手動鏡影得靚唔靚<br />\n<br />\n亦試話有龍友拎枝Wide鏡貼埋去女仔句影<br />\n我要擋走佢，佢重夠面皮話自己記者要交功課"},{"pid":"3fcbba6a4e7fe911c7165f41345a54fd5c85e2eb","tid":129502,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:11:04.000Z","msg":"多樣野打發時間"},{"pid":"8ca51a3c0ceddf2e5f4f94a92e55190ff894eaf8","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔公開咁影黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n影黎自己J</blockquote><br />\nCommercial 會有保密條款<br />\n社運有道德規範<br />\n<br />\n至於丁唔丁，如果海量圖片要處理<br />\n重要同設計同PR傾<br />\n又要就第三方要求比相<br />\n<br />\n咁邊得閒丁相"},{"pid":"c0a193806f5653efff6f9dc29b88b34c8ebe7b33","tid":129502,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daff88aaf4daf0589852ae4523ecf346ffdee654","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多樣野打發時間</blockquote><br />\n幾好既，有時候真係要樣興趣去抒解下自已既生活壓力"},{"pid":"2ff1f22ae34315fe47c2fcf7d6a02fd671d01b98","tid":129502,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔公開咁影黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n諗法唔同啦，又唔係要呃like<br />\n<br />\n如果影低左社運抗爭者既相又周圍貼<br />\n傳聞係會有blacklist既<br />\n<br />\n而且我見太多龍友當社運係影女活動<br />\n前面開晒旗<br />\n佢地可以慢慢討論枝手動鏡影得靚唔靚<br />\n<br />\n亦試話有龍友拎枝Wide鏡貼埋去女仔句影<br />\n我要擋走佢，佢重夠面皮話自己記者要交功課</blockquote><br />\n咁你又影？"},{"pid":"d2bcfb5a3abd4fed0cf5a24f8b41f4830e97af86","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔公開咁影黎做乜？</blockquote><br />\n諗法唔同啦，又唔係要呃like<br />\n<br />\n如果影低左社運抗爭者既相又周圍貼<br />\n傳聞係會有blacklist既<br />\n<br />\n而且我見太多龍友當社運係影女活動<br />\n前面開晒旗<br />\n佢地可以慢慢討論枝手動鏡影得靚唔靚<br />\n<br />\n亦試話有龍友拎枝Wide鏡貼埋去女仔句影<br />\n我要擋走佢，佢重夠面皮話自己記者要交功課</blockquote><br />\n咁你又影？</blockquote><br />\n你都可以影架<br />\n<br />\n因為唔知邊日會出事<br />\n<br />\n而且政府一定有file<br />\n<br />\n被狗咬到就花硬底<br />\n<br />\n你見我不停開post搵人架<br />\n<br />\n不過大部分人一秒都唔使就會screen走之嘛<br />\n<br />\n而且個答案在開頭已經講左<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知為乜"},{"pid":"6f7708d5d97077186ffcfe4b6a7cad5d52c74cf0","tid":129502,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"主要係香港境內郊遊影景<span style=\"color: pink;\">唔通毒撚冇人俾我影又話過你知咩</span><br />\n純粹想郊遊既同時影低一d自己覺得靚/特別既野"},{"pid":"94034d70efdf0dcf8a1c49b0bdf11854cbac7578","tid":129502,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd282c8a9c307df953739ed831eb54b98213e836","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初初玩第一部係菲林傻瓜機,大約小學三年班左右<br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得可以將生out out 會郁既畫面經過相機同菲林再係相紙到重現返出黎好神奇<br />\n<br />\n仲記得果陣小學去旅行,唔識影相既我影出黎張張大頭<br />\n<br />\n但係就影得好開心,咩野生活趣事都拎黎影一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個故事有返童真<br />\n☺️☺️☺️☺️☺️"},{"pid":"817c53f2b0c94d43c8408c8d31a7420ff87b237a","tid":129502,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:56:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43b42793cc3d0955281da9cec025aab6c9e2c6d4","tid":129502,"uid":57146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T19:02:00.000Z","msg":"中學好早就有數碼相機用，算係同學入面比較早有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次有活動都會我揸機同大家影<br />\n後來慢慢少左，大學都係用iphone多<br />\n出黎做野因爲鍾意既人玩開相機<br />\n就突然對影相有翻興趣<br />\n買哂單反咁想影靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f49688836d7b94e371f59bb4a5348a6a5760b31","tid":129502,"uid":47608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T19:49:27.000Z","msg":"同拍左好耐拖既女朋友散左，想搵野散心，就開始拎返樣想學好耐既興趣出黎認真學"},{"pid":"a81209d291489e704609851d8cdf3190fd71b2f7","tid":129502,"uid":5933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:09:38.000Z","msg":"個時去以色列前覺得一定要買部相機記錄低<br />\n返到就愛上咔嚓個一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16ac18165690171320c65433ac9b8ae0fa8b2d3","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同拍左好耐拖既女朋友散左，想搵野散心，就開始拎返樣想學好耐既興趣出黎認真學</blockquote><br />\n😢😢😢巴打別哭"},{"pid":"d577564208ec9f1441ff53e1687dfba1ea5fb080","tid":129502,"uid":10023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為買左部手機有manual mode，對上一部機剩係得auto mode，而且當時我唔知可以裝第三方third-party影相app例如open camera之類</blockquote><br />\n開班未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"903156f4e9fb75aee25fbc9ccd42ec0a3a26dd6b","tid":129502,"uid":19776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"紀錄純潔一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfe06a6fce2e5a147d9301ba38cde783490c20c","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個時去以色列前覺得一定要買部相機記錄低<br />\n返到就愛上咔嚓個一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來旅攝JJ"},{"pid":"e7f0f1f91c6d3b993e031d5c02b72c081edafa5f","tid":129502,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為買左部手機有manual mode，對上一部機剩係得auto mode，而且當時我唔知可以裝第三方third-party影相app例如open camera之類</blockquote><br />\n開班未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n無反都影唔到手機咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求開班"},{"pid":"31a09d32f01d4236d49cbceafeabc08d1ed652b1","tid":129502,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:45:21.000Z","msg":"我影相係因為想紀錄"},{"pid":"e6d1f92283942c2062ee35010b00cb79046e0151","tid":129502,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"巴閉law 疊馬 英雄主義"},{"pid":"115142caae1deb0831a07a28dc4618ef9e93a925","tid":129502,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴閉law 疊馬 英雄主義</blockquote><br />\n呢個答案好野"}]}